\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 12, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ptk1665703174714.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ptk1665703174714.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ptk1665703174714.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ptk1665703174714\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Decode the contents of <code class=\"ph codeph\">InBuf</code> and place the result in <code class=\"ph codeph\">OutBuf</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ptk1665703174714__section_w2092ab1b5b1_w2093ab1b5_w2094ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d979272e55\">Return Values</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"ptk1665703174714__parml_kbw_mtp_dwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">USEC_SUCCESS</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Decode successful, no info returned </dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">USEC_ERROR</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Decode failed, error returned in Error members </dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ptk1665703174714__section_w2095ab1b5b3_w2096ab1b5_w2097ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d979272e82\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ptk1665703174714__p_d132146e1_d132147e1_d132148e1\">Decode the data in <code class=\"ph codeph\">InBuf</code> of length\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">InDataLen</code>. The decoded data must be placed in <code class=\"ph codeph\">OutBuf</code> and\n        its length in <code class=\"ph codeph\">OutDataLen</code>, which must be less than or equal to\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">OutBufLen</code>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ptk1665703174714__p_d132149e1_d132150e1_d132151e1\">If the output buffer is not large enough to hold the\n        decoded data, return an error.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531068\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531068\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "USEC_DECODE Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 12, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Decode the contents of InBuf and place the result in OutBuf . Return Values USEC_SUCCESS Decode successful, no info returned USEC_ERROR Decode failed, error returned in Error members Description Decode the data in InBuf of length InDataLen . The decoded data must be placed in OutBuf and its length in OutDataLen , which must be less than or equal to OutBufLen . If the output buffer is not large enough to hold the decoded data, return an error. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}